4.20	The_Power_of_Darkness	The Power of Darkness	The Power of Darkness (Russian: , Vlast' t'my) is a five-act drama by Leo Tolstoy. Written in 1886, the play's production was forbidden to be produced Russia until 1902, mainly through the influence of in Konstantin Pobedonostsev. In spite of the ban, the play was unofficially produced and read numerous times.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/22/Scene_from_The_Power_of_Darkness.jpg/250px-Scene_from_The_Power_of_Darkness.jpg
